{"tid":1286532,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"以共之矛，攻共之盾！","createTime":"2019-07-05T01:41:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T01:45:43.000Z","uid":76784,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ce210b496ddf79f71f82868573af620a22487b0b","tid":1286532,"uid":76784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T01:41:26.000Z","msg":"&middot; 世界是你們的，也是我們的，但是歸根結底是你們的。你們年青人朝氣蓬勃，正在興旺時候，好像早晨八、九點鍾的太陽。希望寄托在你們身上。 &mdash;&mdash; 毛佳句<br />\n<br />\n 究竟是一個黨好，還是幾個黨好？現在看來，恐怕是幾個黨好。 &mdash;&mdash; 毛佳句<br />\n<br />\n&middot; 人民萬歲！革命無罪，造反有理！ 哪裏有壓迫哪裏就有反抗! 不要被糖衣炮彈打倒 &mdash;&mdash; 毛澤東語錄<br />\n<br />\n&middot; 革命不是請客吃飯，不是做文章，不是繪畫綉花，不能那樣雅致，那樣從容不迫，&ldquo;文質彬彬&rdquo;，那樣&ldquo;溫良恭儉讓&rdquo;。革命就是暴動，是一個階級推翻一個階級的暴烈的行動。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我同我屋企講，佢地即刻收皮！大家參考下！"},{"pid":"761370aed446291b7ce974fcb61f3afdf4f666d3","tid":1286532,"uid":200758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T01:42:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OJfWtfJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOJfWtfJ.jpg&h=3b2d02f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r6QrQt4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr6QrQt4.jpg&h=02ad2ebb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ofWuem.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ofWuem.png&h=f545a766&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eaa5c42b9c6e00b507e6959678d3f57de1deef85","tid":1286532,"uid":263261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T01:44:36.000Z","msg":"支持毛澤東，支持毛語錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"895ea70df289ffb5416ec379d344337d3c4d890b","tid":1286532,"uid":102343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T01:45:43.000Z","msg":"遊行集會讀毛語錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}